      "writtenOn": "2026-03-23T15:22:25Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "LOCK_FAILURE due to failure on the atomic compare-and-update of the branch tip would make the command invalid. That is one way that the command set could be empty. It is ok not to log the info-refs and negotiation time for failed pushes, the overall wall clock time for the command is a reasonable proxy.",
